Secretary: There
is fighting on the ground as we
speak, which

00:40.941 --> 00:45.479 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
is why it's hard for us to have
every single
detail as to what's transpired,
and there's

00:45.512 --> 00:52.019 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
