with a rocket
barrage, while Saudi Arabia
launched new airstrikes

01:21.581 --> 01:28.121 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in a series of cities, including
Sanaa. Residents
of the capital surveyed the
damage today.

01:28.155 --> 01:33.427 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Some accused the Saudis of
hitting civilian
targets, including a health
center for the

01:33.460 --> 01:35.729 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
blind, but there were no
casualties.

01:35.762 --> 01:42.269 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
