scene today,
as the bodies of dozens more
migrants washed

01:42.302 --> 01:48.508 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
up on shore. Authorities say at
least 36 people
drowned when their boats
capsized in the Aegean

01:48.542 --> 01:54.948 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Sea trying to reach Greece.
Turkish crews
found the victims strewn along
beaches. They

01:54.982 --> 02:00.787 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
