Organization for
Migration: Migrants and refugees
continue

02:05.826 --> 02:11.465 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to enter Greece at a rate of
over 2,500 a
day from Turkey, which is very
close to the

02:11.498 --> 02:17.704 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
average through December, so we
see the migrant
flows are continuing through the
winter, and,

02:17.738 --> 02:20.874 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
